edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.database

Interface NoSQLRecords

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CassandraRecords, DiskMapRecords, MongoRecords

    public interface NoSQLRecords
    Provides an interface for insert, update, remove and lookup operations in a nosql database.
    Author:
    Westy

                                       ColumnField valuesMapField,
                                       String key,
                                       String value,
